{
  "texts": [
    "It finally combined different features and predicted that the participant is in a sad mood.",
    "These cases showed the capability of MultiEEG-GPT to (1) analyze each modality separately, (2) aggregated the outputs based on different modalities jointly.",
    "It is also evident that a single modality is not adequate to identify the mood correctly.",
    "For example, MultiEEG-GPT identified the status of Figure 1 (b) as \"an emotional reaction\".",
    "However, it did not accurately state that the participant is sad from the EEG features."
  ]
}